## Testing Class Methods

```ruby
test "trending returns popular articles" do
  trending = Article.trending
  
  assert trending.count > 0
  assert trending.all? { |a| a.views_count > 1000 }
end

test "search finds articles by title" do
  results = Article.search("First")
  
  assert results.count > 0
  assert results.any? { |a| a.title.include?("First") }
end
```

